As per the PDPL, the Saudi Data and Artificial Intelligence Authority ("SDAIA") will be the data regulator for at least two years. During this time, consideration will be given to transferring the competence to supervise the application of the PDPL (and its Executive Regulations) to the NDMO.&nbsp;
The Saudi Central Bank and the Communications and Information Technology Commission ("CITC") both appear to maintain their jurisdiction to regulate data protection within their remit.Last modified 17 Jan 2022
				
			